Puppet module: activemq

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages activemq software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include activemq              # Install and run activemq with standard configurations.
include activemq::disable     # Disable activemq service.
include activemq::disableboot # Disable activemq service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include activemq::absent      # Remove activemq package.

DEPENDENCIES:
